			<h3>
				<span>Read more on </span>
                			<span class="tag">
			<a href="/web/20101121051608/http://www.bbc.com/travel/usa" rel="tag">USA</a>
		</span>
				</h3>
			<ul>
                				<li>
					<a class="link" href="/web/20101121051608/http://www.bbc.com/travel/feature/20101103-from-warhol-to-wright-an-arty-trip-through-pennsylvania">
                        From Warhol to Wright                    </a>
					<p>An art and architecture road trip through western Pennsylvania</p>
                                        <a href="/web/20101121051608/http://www.bbc.com/travel/feature/20101103-from-warhol-to-wright-an-arty-trip-through-pennsylvania">
                        <img alt="Fallingwater" src="/web/20101121051608im_/http://static.bbc.co.uk/wwtravel/img/ic/144-81/12892491396904191573_1.jpg" />
                    </a>
                    				</li>
                				<li>
					<a class="link" href="/web/20101121051608/http://www.bbc.com/travel/blog/20101117-travelwise-iconic-road-trips-in-film-and-literature">
                        Iconic movie and book road trips                    </a>
					<p>A few exciting road trips in contemporary film and literature.</p>
